  - FITNESS = DS_COLORS.ACCENT_PRIMARY (#E8593C)
  - MIND = #4A5568 (slate)
  - DISCIPLINE = DS_COLORS.ACCENT_GREEN (#2D7A4F)

### Button Rules
```
Primary CTA:  DS_COLORS.ACCENT_PRIMARY bg, white text, height 56, borderRadius 14
Success CTA:  DS_COLORS.ACCENT_GREEN bg, white text, height 56, borderRadius 14
Dark CTA:     #111111 bg, white text, height 56, borderRadius 14
Destructive:  #DC2626 bg, white text, height 56, borderRadius 14
